138
00:07:57,580 --> 00:08:00,680
Saya yakin dia masih ada rancangan lain.

139
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:05,779
Bila difikirkan, kita tak sempat membunuh dia.

140
00:08:05,780 --> 00:08:07,279
Ya.

141
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:09,879
Saya yakin bahawa dia akan muncul

142
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:13,279
semasa kita mendapatkan Kir kembali.

143
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:17,280
Mungkin dia memang lelaki jenis begitu?

144
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:49,379
Jadi juruhebah Rena Mizunashi itu ialah ejen CIA?

145
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:50,679
Ya.

146
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:54,879
Disebabkan dia bersetuju untuk kembali kepada Organisasi Hitam itu,

147
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:57,479
