157
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:19,579
Tidak.

158
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:21,579
Saya dengar bahawa dia tak mahukannya.

159
00:09:21,580 --> 00:09:22,779
Walaupun ejen-ejen FBI itu

160
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:24,979
