Dia meminati budak perempuan

197
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:43,179
atau benda seperti itu?

198
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:44,779
Maksud kamu, tekaan saya betul?

199
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:45,980
Kamu sangat dungu.

200
